# Athens Master Tech Kit
**Outside Inn Studios | Mar–May 2026 | Living Document**

> Single master reference for all hardware, software, streaming infrastructure, simulcast strategy, recording strategy, and accumulated issue/fix history. Optimized for AI project context and GitHub. Supersedes `AthensTechStack03_31_2026.md`. Update when anything changes.

---

## QUICK REFERENCE — CONFIRMED WORKING STATE

```
Machine         GIGABYTE AERO X16 — Ryzen AI 7 350, RTX 5070 Laptop, 32GB DDR5, Win 11
Stream path     OBS → Restream.io (Europe - Frankfurt) → YouTube (@EIWerner) + Twitch (@eiwerner)
Bitrate         4500 kbps CBR — confirmed safe ceiling for this connection
Keyframe        2 seconds — required by Restream
Camera          Elgato Facecam MK.2 — physical device in OBS (not Elgato Virtual Camera)
Gameplay        Window Capture — WoW in Borderless Windowed (not Game Capture)
Titles          Always via Restream Update Titles — never YouTube Studio or Twitch directly
Chat            Twitch popout on laptop + YouTube Studio on iPad
Recording       Source Record (camera ISO + gameplay ISO) + OBS built-in (full canvas)
VPS             DigitalOcean → Restream → YouTube 24/7 lo-fi radio (separate stream slot)
SSD             D:\StreamSourceFiles\ (SanDisk 2TB Extreme)
```

