## 5. GO-LIVE CHECKLIST

### Pre-Stream

```
[ ] Confirm lo-fi VPS is NOT streaming — separate Restream slot, conflicts if both run (C13)
[ ] Restream → app.restream.io → Update Titles — title + category for both platforms
[ ] Verify OBS Stream settings:
      Service    = Restream.io
      Server     = Europe - Frankfurt   ← never Autodetect (C1)
      Bitrate    = 4500 kbps            ← never higher (C2)
      Keyframe   = 2 seconds            ← required (C3)
[ ] Verify camera source = Elgato Facecam MK.2 (not Elgato Virtual Camera) (C5)
[ ] Camera Hub: open → verify settings → Save → X out → quit fully from system tray (C6)
[ ] YouTube Studio: confirm stream privacy (Unlisted for tests, Public for live)
[ ] Twitch Dashboard: confirm channel is ready — no title edit needed
```

### Going Live

```
[ ] OBS → Start Streaming
      ↳ Source Record (camera ISO) auto-starts
      ↳ Source Record (gameplay ISO) auto-starts
[ ] OBS → Start Recording    ← manual step for full canvas (C14)
[ ] OBS bottom bar: dropped frames < 2% within 60 seconds — if climbing, see troubleshooting
[ ] Chat: Twitch popout (laptop) + YouTube Studio (iPad)
```

### Post-Stream

```
[ ] OBS → Stop Recording     ← full canvas
[ ] OBS → Stop Streaming
      ↳ Source Record filters stop automatically
[ ] Remux MKV → MP4:
      OBS → File → Remux Recordings → select all three MKV files → Remux
      Keep MKV originals until remux confirmed clean
[ ] Move files to dated archive folder
```

