## 7. VPS — LO-FI RADIO

| Field | Value |
|---|---|
| **Provider** | DigitalOcean (Ubuntu, 1GB RAM) |
| **Function** | FFmpeg looping `HoldtLoop.mp4` → Restream → YouTube 24/7 |
| **Stream key** | Separate Restream slot — distinct from live stream key |
| **Known issue** | No auto-restart loop — if Restream drops connection, FFmpeg process dies |
| **Priority** | High — implement shell loop wrapper before next extended absence |

> ⚠️ Confirm lo-fi VPS is NOT streaming before starting any live stream. Two sources on the same Restream account simultaneously can cause conflicts. (C13)

