## 11. AI CONTEXT NOTES

- **Streaming machine:** AERO X16 (AMD Ryzen AI 7 350, RTX 5070 Laptop, 32GB DDR5, Windows 11)
- **Simulcast:** OBS → Restream.io (Europe - Frankfurt) → YouTube (@EIWerner) + Twitch (@eiwerner). Confirmed working March 31, 2026.
- **Recording:** Source Record (camera ISO + gameplay ISO, auto-start) + OBS built-in (full canvas, manual start). All local to SanDisk SSD. Zero stream bandwidth impact.
- **Titles:** Always Restream Update Titles — never platform dashboards directly.
- **Camera:** Elgato Facecam MK.2, physical device in OBS. Camera Hub not needed during streams; quit via system tray pre-stream.
- **Gameplay:** Window Capture only — WoW in Borderless Windowed. Never Game Capture.
- **Bitrate ceiling:** 4500 kbps — apartment actual upload is 8–10 Mbps despite 19 Mbps nominal.
- **Server:** Europe - Frankfurt — hardcoded, never Autodetect.
- **Dropped frames counter:** Cumulative per OBS session — restart for clean read.
- **Lo-fi radio:** DigitalOcean VPS → separate Restream slot → YouTube 24/7. Must not run during live streams.
- **SSD:** All stream files at `D:\StreamSourceFiles\`

